name: Unnatural Selection (itch) (C1rcu1t)
description:
In a post-apocalyptic world, factions of different species fight to control a machine which changes the climate of the world. Thus creating the phenomenon, unnatural selection. Play as one of the four factions!

Insect Faction - Expendable.

Mech Faction - Powerful.

Rocks - Bulky.

Shadows - Bloodthirsty.

Feedback form: https://tinyurl.com/UnnaturalSelectionFeedback
